data.description: Located in the well-established East Main neighborhood, Woodland Cottage overlooks a serene conservation area while offering close proximity to Seabrook’s Town Center. This cottage features an enclosed sunroom that is ideal for enjoying sunny coastal days and storms alike. From the sunroom, be greeted by the well-equipped kitchen with custom cabinetry that flows seamlessly into the living room bathed in natural light. The main floor segue ways to a private, covered deck. Down the stairs you will find the primary bedroom with easy access to the patio area, as well as a guest bedroom and shared bathroom.
